caption: Only my shadow knows how I feel about Jack and Jack ???#contest I have been literally waited a long time to meet Jack and Jack and have been watching their Vines and hearing all their amazing songs which really impacted me to make a change and impact many people's life which as seen in many of their songs they write and one of my favorites has to be tides because that one shows me that even though people may push you down and make you feel less you have to rise from all that and follow your dreams  lastly I just wanted to say I can never really afford to go to any of their meet and greets and concerns which I have been eager to see I cry thinking that I won't be able to see them and now since my family is going through some income issues this will really make my dreams come a reality
